00:43:14.880 --> 00:43:18.710
to

00:43:18.720 --> 00:43:22.030
God! We thank you, Father, for

00:43:22.040 --> 00:43:24.470
the breakthrough.

00:43:29.040 --> 00:43:32.470
2025

00:43:32.470 --> 00:43:32.480
is

00:43:32.480 --> 00:43:34.589
